Atomic Electronic Spin Populations:
----------------------------------
  N_alpha(A) = Average number of Alpha electrons in Atom A
  N_beta(A) = Average number of Beta electrons in Atom A
  N_total(A) = N_alpha(A) + N_beta(A)
  N_spin(A) = N_alpha(A) - N_beta(A)
